---
title: Thai Sweet Chilli Pork Bowl with Peanut Rice & Sautéed Veggies
description: It's a good thing this Thai dish is quick and easy to make, because it smells so amazing as it cooks that it's tempting to eat it straight from the pan! But it's worth the wait, especially for the sweet chilli glaze which has got to be the tastiest sauce around.
